(1053, 1, 'page', '{\"name\":\"GroPart Policies\",\"slug\":\"gropart-policy\",\"slug_id\":\"98\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"description\":null,\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<div class=\\\"ps-deal-of-day ps-block--countdown-deal\\\"><div class=\\\"ps-section__header ps-block__left\\\"><h3>GroPart Policies<\\/h3><\\/div><\\/div><p style=\\\"line-height:1.38;margin-bottom:12pt;margin-top:12pt;\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span><strong>Return, Refund and Exchange Policy:&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height:1.38;margin-bottom:12pt;margin-top:12pt;\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#111111;\\\"><span>Gropart\\u2019s Return Policy offers no return of goods once delivered.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><ul><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>Buyer will be eligible for a return, when he receives the damaged product, receives the wrong product and quantity varies.&nbsp;And for this you have to inform our customer service centre within 24 hours.<\\/span><\\/span><br>&nbsp;<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>Items must be unused and in the same condition that you received it. It must also be in the original packaging. We require a receipt or proof of purchase and the buyer must have made a video of the product\'s packaging during open.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><br>&nbsp;<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>In case you feel that the product received is not as shown on the site or as per your expectations, you must bring it to the notice of our customer service within 24 hours of receiving the product. The Customer Service Team after looking into your complaint will take an appropriate decision.<\\/span><\\/span><br>&nbsp;<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>If the customer damages the product, we will cross check with our photos and videos. If there is buyer\\u2019s fault then nothing will be refunded.<\\/span><\\/span><br>&nbsp;<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>If both seller and buyer have not damaged the product, the carrier will be at fault and appropriate action will be taken against them and customer will be refunded but a&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"background-color:#f8f9fa;color:#202124;\\\"><span>video must be made while opening the packaging of the product by buyer.<\\/span><\\/span><br>&nbsp;<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>If the buyer really gets the damaged product by our side then we will give a full refund to the customer or we will ask for an exchange if customer agrees then we will exchange the product at no extra cost.<\\/span><\\/span><br>&nbsp;<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>If you are approved, then your refund will be processed, and a credit will automatically be applied to your credit card or original method of payment, within a certain amount of days.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><br>&nbsp;<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>If you haven\\u2019t received a refund yet, first check your bank account again. Then contact your credit card company, it may take some time before your refund is officially posted. Next contact your bank. Normally your refund will be credited into your account within 7-10 days working days.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>There is often some processing time before a refund is posted. If you\\u2019ve done all of this and you still have not received your refund yet, please contact us at +91-7357845792<\\/span><\\/span><br>&nbsp;<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#111111;\\\"><span>Products must be returned within 7 days from the day of delivery. To return your purchase, please call customer care at +91-7357845792 within 24 hours.<\\/span><\\/span><br>&nbsp;<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>Our policy lasts 15 days. If 15 days have gone by since your purchase, unfortunately, we can\'t offer you a refund. If the return policy happens then we will send you an email to notify you that we have received your returned item. We will also notify you of the approval or rejection of your refund as per conditions.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><br>&nbsp;<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#111111;\\\"><span>To request a refund, simply call on +91-7357845792&nbsp; with your purchase details within seven (7) days of your purchase. Please include your order number (sent to you via email\\/message after ordering) and optionally tell us why you\\u2019re requesting a refund \\u2013 we take customer feedback very seriously and use it to constantly improve our products and quality of service.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li><\\/ul><p style=\\\"line-height:1.38;margin-bottom:12pt;margin-left:36pt;margin-top:12pt;\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#111111;\\\"><span>Refunds are being processed after the customer support team validate and analyse the issue, but it will only show in your bank account only when the product comes back to the hub. Once the refund is processed we will intimate you through EMAIL and SMS with the refund transaction details&nbsp;The refund is only possible if the product is unused or damaged, and is with the original packaging and with the receipt and the invoice. Only when the product reaches the premises will we refund you your amount as decided.<\\/span><\\/span><br>&nbsp;<\\/p><ul><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#ff0000;\\\"><span>NEED TO CONFIRM ABOUT THIS: It\'s your responsibility to take out a print of the manifest that Gropart provides, while returning the product.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li><\\/ul><p style=\\\"line-height:1.38;margin-bottom:12pt;margin-top:12pt;\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span><strong>Shipping and Delivery Policy:<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><ul><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;\\\"><span>Gropart&nbsp; is committed to deliver your order with good quality packaging within a given time frame. We ship throughout the week, except Sunday &amp; Public holidays. To ensure that your order reaches you in good condition, in the shortest span of time, we ship through reputed courier agencies only. If there is no courier service available in your area, we will ship your items via postal service.. We ship only around India.<\\/span><\\/span><br>&nbsp;<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;\\\"><span>The shipping charge is specified separately for every product. For multiple products ordered the programme adds up the total of all individual shipping charges. Thus, a customer who orders three products is charged the total of all individual delivery charges associated with each product. Thus the delivery fee is calculated separately when a customer orders different products.<\\/span><\\/span><br>&nbsp;<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#505050;\\\"><span>Once our system processes your order; your products are inspected thoroughly to ensure they are in a perfect condition. After they pass through the quality check, they are packed and handed over to our trusted delivery partner. Our delivery partners then bring the package to you at the earliest possible.<\\/span><\\/span><br>&nbsp;<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;\\\"><span>Orders are dispatched within 3 working days or as per the delivery date specified by you at the time of placing the order. Most orders are delivered within 7 to 8 working days or earlier. Delivery of all orders will be duly done to the address as mentioned by you at the time of placing the order.<\\/span><\\/span><br>&nbsp;<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;\\\"><span>If you think you have received the product in a bad condition or if the packaging is tampered with or damaged before delivery, please refuse to accept the package and return the package to the delivery person. Also, please call our customer care at 7357845792 mentioning your Order ID. We will personally ensure that a brand new replacement is issued to you with no additional cost. Please make sure that the original product tag and packing is intact when you send us the product back.<\\/span><\\/span><br>&nbsp;<\\/l