bsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><ul><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>By agreeing to these Terms of Service, you represent that you are at least the age of majority in your state or province of residence, or that you are the age of majority in your state or province of residence and you have given us your consent to allow any of your minor dependents to use this site.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>We sell many kinds of&nbsp; <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#202124;\\\"><span>hazardous items&nbsp; <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>on our website. We strictly do not allow children to buy.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>You may not use our products for any illegal or unauthorised purpose nor may you, in the use of the Service, violate any laws in your jurisdiction (including but not limited to copyright laws).&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>You must not transmit any worms or viruses or any code of a destructive nature.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>A breach or violation of any of the Terms will result in an immediate termination of your Services.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li><\\/ul><p style=\\\"line-height:1.38;text-align:justify;\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#111111;\\\"><span><strong>Communications:<\\/strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height:1.38;text-align:justify;\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>When You use the Platform or send emails or other data, information or communication to us, You agree, believe and understand that You are communicating with Gropart through electronic records and You consent to receive communications via electronic records from us periodically and as and when required. We may communicate with you by email, SMS or by other modes of communication, electronic or otherwise.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height:1.38;text-align:justify;\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#111111;\\\"><span><strong>General Conditions:<\\/strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><ul><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>We reserve the right to refuse service to anyone for any reason at any time.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>You understand that your content (not including credit card information), may be transferred unencrypted and involve (a) transmissions over various networks; and (b) changes to conform and adapt to technical requirements of connecting networks or devices. Credit card information is always encrypted during transfer over networks.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>You agree not to reproduce, duplicate, copy, sell, resell or exploit any portion of the Service, use of the Service, or access to the Service or any contact on the website through which the service is provided, without express written permission by us.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>The headings used in this agreement are included for convenience only and will not limit or otherwise affect these Terms.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li><\\/ul><p style=\\\"line-height:1.38;text-align:justify;\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#111111;\\\"><span><strong>Company Internal Trading:<\\/strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><br><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>Gropart.com is a multi vendor ecommerce platform where it\\u2019s parent company is also selling its product on the website.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><br><br><span style=\\\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#111111;\\\"><span><strong>Product and Services:<\\/strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><br><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>Gropart is not responsible for unsatisfactory or delayed performance of services or damages or delays as a result of products which are out of stock, unavailable or back ordered.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height:1.38;text-align:justify;\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>All Products sold on Gropart are Premium Quality. Products sold on the platform are purchased via legal channels or directly from the Company. Agrowala holds no liability or responsibility for the performance of any product.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height:1.38;text-align:justify;\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span>Disclaimer: Pricing on any product(s) as is reflected on the Platform may due to some technical issue, typographical error or product information published by Agrowala may be incorrectly reflected and in such an event Agrowala may cancel such order(s).&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height:1.38;text-align:justify;\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\">&nbsp;<\\