(2, 'About Us', '<div class=\"ps-deal-of-day ps-block--countdown-deal\"><div class=\"ps-section__header ps-block__left\"><h3>About us</h3></div></div><p style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"><span>Gropart.com where sellers can advertise to promote and sell their products relevant to agriculture and commercial machines, thus we act as a bridge between sellers and buyers for agricultural input products and products of commercial machines.&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"><span>We are known for supplying Agriculture Equipment and Parts, Farming Tools, Parts of Farming Vehicle, Parts of Commercial Machines and Machine Implements that are required in agriculture and commercial fields. We provide guaranteed market\'s best price and customer support with Home Delivery throughout India. Gropart comes under a company named S.B. Marketing. This is the parent company of Gropart and working as a Seller on Gropart platform.</span></span><br>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"><span>Under the mentoring of our managing director, Mr________we have been able to satisfy huge clientele across India. Assisted by our excellent management skills, we are one of the fastest-growing companies in India</span></span></p>', 1, NULL, 'default', 0, NULL, 'published', '2022-01-03 21:24:05', '2022-06-21 18:10:15');
